  <entry>
    <title>算法题012排序</title>
    <url>/2020/07/28/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E9%A2%98012%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>一个数组只有0,1,2三种元素，不允许使用额外空间，每个元素只许遍历一次，将这个数组从小到大排序 </p>
<a id="more"></a> 
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x2F;**</span><br><span class="line"> * @ClassName main</span><br><span class="line"> * @Description TODO</span><br><span class="line"> * @Author Li Guicheng</span><br><span class="line"> * @Date 2020&#x2F;7&#x2F;28 16:46</span><br><span class="line"> * @Version 1.0</span><br><span class="line"> **&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">public class main &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        int[] arr &#x3D; &#123;1, 1, 1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 2, 0, 1, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 0, 0&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">        int[] arr1 &#x3D; sort(arr);</span><br><span class="line">        for (int i &#x3D; 0; i &lt; arr1.length; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            System.out.print(arr1[i] + &quot;   &quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#x2F;&#x2F;思想就是把0，2分别往两边放</span><br><span class="line">    public static int[] sort(int[] num) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        int locOf0 &#x3D; 0;</span><br><span class="line">        int locOf2 &#x3D; num.length - 1;</span><br><span class="line">        int order &#x3D; 0;</span><br><span class="line">        int temp;</span><br><span class="line">        &#x2F;&#x2F;order顺序迭代下去，locOf2之后的全部都是2了，不需要继续了</span><br><span class="line">        for (; order &lt;&#x3D; locOf2; order++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            &#x2F;&#x2F;遇到0，把它往边上放，如果换回来的是2的话，要把2放到后面去</span><br><span class="line">            if(num[order] &#x3D;&#x3D; 0) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                while(num[locOf0] &#x3D;&#x3D; 0) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    locOf0++;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                temp &#x3D; num[locOf0];</span><br><span class="line">                num[locOf0] &#x3D; num[order];</span><br><span class="line">                num[order] &#x3D; temp;</span><br><span class="line">                locOf0++;</span><br><span class="line">                if(num[order] &#x3D;&#x3D; 2) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    while(num[locOf2] &#x3D;&#x3D; 2) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        locOf2--;</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    temp &#x3D; num[locOf2];</span><br><span class="line">                    num[locOf2] &#x3D; num[order];</span><br><span class="line">                    num[order] &#x3D; temp;</span><br><span class="line">                    locOf2--;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;else if(num[order] &#x3D;&#x3D; 2) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                while(num[locOf2] &#x3D;&#x3D; 2) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    locOf2--;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                temp &#x3D; num[locOf2];</span><br><span class="line">                num[locOf2] &#x3D; num[order];</span><br><span class="line">                num[order] &#x3D; temp;</span><br><span class="line">                locOf2--;                </span><br><span class="line">                if(num[order] &#x3D;&#x3D; 0) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    while(num[locOf0] &#x3D;&#x3D; 0) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                        locOf0++;</span><br><span class="line">                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    temp &#x3D; num[locOf0];</span><br><span class="line">                    num[locOf0] &#x3D; num[order];</span><br><span class="line">                    num[order] &#x3D; temp;</span><br><span class="line">                    locOf0++;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        return num;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>结果图：<br><img src="/images/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%951.png" alt="结果"></p>
]]></content>
